high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the toilet.
Pick up the pink spray bottle from the top of the toilet.
Turn around and face the bath tub.
Place the spray bottle on the bath tub.
Turn right and walk towards the toilet.
Pick up the pink spray bottle from the top of the toilet.
Turn around and face the bath tub.
Place the spray bottle on the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Place the two bottles from the top of toilet to the top of the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the right of the toilet
Grab a spray bottle off of the top of the toilet
Move slightly to the left and look at the tub
Put the bottle on the counter to the right of the tub
Move slightly to the right and face the toilet
Grab the spray bottle off of the top of the toilet
Move slightly to the left and look at the tub
Put the bottle on the counter to the right of the tub
anns.task_desc: Putting two spray bottles on the counter near the tub

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the toilet tank.
Pick up the purple bottle on the left side of the tank.
Take a step to the left from where you are at.
Place the bottle on the bath tub countertop.
Take a step to the right from where you are at.
Pick up the other purple bottle from the toilet tank.
Take a step to the left from where you are at.
Place the bottle next to the other bottle on the bath tub countertop.
anns.task_desc: Transfer the two purple bottles from the toilet tank to the bath tub countertop.
